	<h2C>Biography</h2C><br>
    <div class="lrgblacktext">
	 
Born in 
 Greensboro on January 19, 1963; educated at Virginia Tech (B.A.); Washington &amp; Lee University School of Law (J.D.); Attorney; married to Lila A. Peake; Methodist; Member of the Senate: 2017-   
